Amazon Top 50 Best Selling Books¶

by Mercy Faith Nyambura Kariuki

Introduction¶

Dataset on Amazon's Top 50 bestselling books from 2009 to 2019. Contains 550 books, data has been categorized into fiction and non-fiction using Goodreads

bestsellers with categories.csv data description:

  • Name - the name of the book
  • Author - the author of the book
  • User Rating - user rating of the book
  • Reviews - reviews given by users of the books
  • Price - price of the book (in dollars)
  • Year - year of realease
  • Genre - genre of the book

Stages of the project

  • 1. Data Aquisition
  • 2. Data Preprocessing
  • 3. ExploratoryDataAnalysis
  • 4. Research Results

    Let's examine the data provided for the project.

    def density_plot(books,col):
    fig=plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))
    sns.kdeplot(books[col],color='blue',shade=True)
    plt.show()
    In [78]:
    density_plot(books,'Price')

    The descriptive statistics show the average price of the books is at 11. The graph shows the distribution of prices to be skewed to the right with most books bought at a price range of 4 - 14

    Top Rated Affordable Books¶

    In [101]:
    #Plot 3: Below plot shows the top authors whose books costs less with highest user ratings
# plt.figure(figsize=(15,15))
books['count'] = 1
books_affordable = books.loc[books['User Rating'] > 4].sort_values('User Rating', ascending = False).sort_values('Price', ascending = True)
sns.relplot(data = books_affordable[:25], x = 'User Rating', 
            y = 'Author', 
            hue = 'Genre', 
            aspect = 2)

#xlabel
plt.xlabel("User Rating", fontsize=15)

#ylabel
plt.ylabel("Author Name", fontsize=15)

#plot title
plt.title("Top Authors With Affordable Books and High User Rating", fontsize=15, weight="bold")
plt.show()

    This grap shows that most of the high rated authors belong to the Fiction Genre. In this case, Alice Schertle, Jeff Kinney, Harper Lee, rick Riodarn and Craig Smith as the top 5 highest rated, with Alice Schertle as the top rated Author. When it comes to Non-fiction Authors, Majorie Sarmat and Delegates of the Constitutional are the top two highest.
